attributionInfo.brokerName: MV Realty of North Carolina LLC

data.description:
Spacious, well-maintained 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath former model home in desirable Windy Ridge Community. Main level boasts open floor plan, office (or separate guest suite), walk in pantry, & 9 ft ceilings throughout. Kitchen has upgraded finishes, stainless steel appliances, white cabinets, separate seating area, updated lighting fixtures & and a beautiful Muscadine Grape vine outside the window. Large inviting family room with gas fireplace, open to kitchen. Upstairs find laundry room a large bonus room and 4 bedrooms, full bathroom, Primary bedroom with built-in storage and ensuite bath and walk in closet. Move-in ready, entire yard Irrigation, new roof in 2022. Major shopping & entertainment areas on route 74 (Target, Walmart, Monroe Mall) and Rocky River Elementary, Private Schools & Charter Schools (Union Academy), Carolina Fitness Ctr, & Monroe Aquatic Center all within 3 miles.

**Seller offering  2-1 Buydown credit w/acceptable offer. Please see photos/attachments for details.**
